headline: Mizuho Maintains Buy Rating and $60 PT on EQT Corporation (EQT)
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) is one of the most undervalued large cap stocks to buy right now. On October 28, Mizuho Securities analyst Nitin Kumar maintained a Buy rating on EQT with a price target of $60.00. Earlier, on October 15, William Blair initiated coverage of EQT Corporation with an Outperform rating but no price target. […]
